By: Zhuangzi
Locus:
  Chapter: 11
  Paragraph: 31
Title: Let It Be, Leave It Alone
---
Cloud Chief said, "Heavenly Master, it has been hard indeed for me to
meet with you - I beg one word of instruction!"
